1
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:22,840
Hey fam,

2
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,359
right now we're on the bus

3
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:26,040
heading to Donghu Park.

4
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:28,760
Ladies, are you doing the East Lake Jump today?

5
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,079
We'll see.

6
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:30,599
We'll see how it goes. It depends on Xiao Yin.

7
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,519
But Xiao Yin definitely isn't jumping.

8
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,719
She's counting on this modern Chinese-style dress

9
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:36,120
to stun the whole crowd.

10
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:41,640
Welcome everyone to this year's East Lake Jump!

11
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,159
Let me hear some noise!

12
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,719
Not enough, not enough!

13
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:47,239
Let's make some noise!

14
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:53,000
Our annual East Lake Jump,

15
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,799
I know everyone's been looking forward to it.

16
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:57,840
Let's take this hot afternoon

17
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:01,079
and cool down this summer!

18
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:03,040
Man, seriously. I give up.

19
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,959
Bro, hurry, hurry!

20
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,480
What are you doing?

21
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,479
What took you so long?

22
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,479
I've got a family to support.

23
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:12,479
Unlike a loafer like you.

24
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,199
Hurry, come with me, quick.

25
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:15,439
Is Xurui here?

26
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,479
Not yet.

27
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,439
She's the team leader,

28
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,520
so she has to come on the school bus.

29
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,280
Wait, what's wrong with you?

30
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,000
Don't tell me you chickened out.

31
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:23,120
I didn't chicken out.

32
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,360
A couple of days ago,

33
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:26,240
there was a misunderstanding.

34
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,560
I'm afraid she doesn't want to see me.

35
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,840
Maybe I shouldn't come.

36
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:30,120
What happened?

37
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,400
Just a bit of a misunderstanding.

38
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:33,919
Bro, what are you talking about?

39
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:35,199
Anyway, no matter what,

40
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,719
just listen to me today.

41
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:38,280
Everything is under my control.

42
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,319
After today,

43
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:40,759
I guarantee she'll change her mind about you.

44
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,360
For real?

45
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:41,960
Let's go.

46
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:42,759
Come on.

47
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,439
It's all arranged.

48
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:46,479
Bro.

49
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:46,840
Where is it?

50
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,159
Stand here.

51
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,639
Open your eyes wide and get ready.

52
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,319
Is this cool or what?

53
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:01,759
A yellow bike and a camera.

54
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,120
You jump while riding it.

55
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:04,240
Surprised, aren't you?

56
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,639
That's not all, there's more.

57
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:06,919
Here.

58
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:07,759
Hold this.

59
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:09,919
Hold it, come on.

60
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:12,039
One, two, there you go!

61
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:12,919
Lin Xurui,

62
00:03:13,199 --> 00:03:14,400
in life I'm yours,

63
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,919
in death I'm your ghost.

64
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:17,400
Kong Xiaocan.

65
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,240
What are you doing?

66
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,000
No, wait.

67
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:20,520
You didn't chicken out, did you?

68
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:22,199
Bro, don't chicken out!

69
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,000
Are you crazy?

70
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,800
If you don't go now,

71
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,240
you won't even qualify to be a ghost. Keep it down!

72
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,000
Only a psycho would ride that thing.

73
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:27,960
Look,

74
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,560
if you don't charge now,

75
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,719
you'll really be a dead ghost.

76
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:44,560
Excuse me,

77
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:46,039
could you move in one seat?

78
00:03:46,039 --> 00:03:46,960
I'd like to sit here for a bit.

79
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,360
Thanks, thank you.

80
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,599
Xiaorui.

81
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:01,719
About that... about Xiaocan.

82
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:02,439
Well, I...

83
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:05,479
I have something to discuss with her.

84
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:06,639
I'll go... go over there.

85
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,439
I'm his mom

86
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,519
I had a serious illness

87
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,680
and used a miracle drug that was still in testing

88
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:26,959
which turned me into this

89
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,600
I know I look a bit young

90
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:38,920
Auntie

91
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,040
I...

92
00:04:41,879 --> 00:04:43,240
Look at this mess I've made

93
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:45,079
It's all a misunderstanding

94
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,279
Xiaorui

95
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:48,519
Xiaocan really didn't mean to betray you

96
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:50,079
He's lucky to have met you

97
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,360
How could he betray you?

98
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:52,600
It's all my fault

99
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:53,879
I didn't explain things clearly

100
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,399
That child, Xiaocan...

101
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,480
he just doesn't know how to cherish things

102
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,600
Plus, our family went through such a big ordeal

103
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:00,800
Xiaorui

104
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,959
For Auntie's sake

105
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:05,480
please give Xiaocan another chance, okay?

106
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:12,759
A-Auntie

107
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,000
I'm sorry

108
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:22,839
A...

109
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:25,759
I'm sorry, Auntie

110
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:27,959
I'm sorry

111
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:31,680
I'm sorry

112
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,319
Xiaorui!

113
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,199
Xiaorui, it's all a misunderstanding!

114
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,240
Darn it

115
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,240
Xurui won't even mention Xiaocan now

116
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:48,360
I messed up a perfectly good situation

117
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,879
Xiaocan, Mom is sorry

118
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:56,920
Hello?

119
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:59,120
Junior Kong, come find me as soon as you get off

120
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,920
I have a job for you wearing a mascot suit

121
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,000
Find someone else for this job

122
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:03,040
Don't be so quick to refuse

123
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,800
When we elect the Deputy Head next year

124
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,720
you'll know how important

125
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,439
these daily efforts are

126
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,519
I really don't want to go

127
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:09,759
Wear it yourself if you want

128
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:18,319
It'd fit you perfectly

129
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,680
It's practically custom-made for you

130
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:22,560
Your task

131
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:23,480
is very simple

132
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,920
Just put on this suit

133
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,759
walk around in the crowd

134
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,759
shout a bit, and jump around

135
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,720
But remember the key movements

136
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,000
I'll teach you. Come on

137
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,160
Hunch over

138
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:36,600
Bend your knees

139
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,360
Most importantly, curl your hands

140
00:06:39,879 --> 00:06:40,199
Jump

141
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,680
Very good

142
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:44,120
Head on

143
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,040
Go on

144
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:51,079
Guys, I'm taking you to see the East Lake Jump

145
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:52,199
Are the warriors ready?

146
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:57,480
Let's have our first warrior jump!

147
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,800
There, there, there!

148
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,519
That looks so fun

149
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:09,000
I want to play with them too

150
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:15,839
Right

151
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:16,839
Jump

152
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:17,920
Jump up!

153
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,439
Go!

154
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,399
Go steal the spotlight!

155
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:25,480
I'm roasting in here

156
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:29,160
Is our second warrior ready?

157
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:29,839
Look!

158
00:07:31,079 --> 00:07:33,959
Turkey head! Turkey head! Turkey head!

159
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,240
The second warrior

160
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,680
That's a very unique look

161
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:42,040
So cool!

162
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,439
This one...

163
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:43,040
How was the jump?

164
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:47,120
I guess it only scores points for style

165
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,480
Our third one...

166
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:48,959
Is there another?

167
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,040
Number three! Number three! Number three!

168
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,600
Let's go!

169
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:46,159
It's a female warrior

170
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:48,519
Look, it's a girl

171
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,240
Even a girl dares to jump

172
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,679
She's so brave. Go for it!

173
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:53,360
Go for it!

174
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,000
Today

175
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,679
That's amazing

176
00:08:57,679 --> 00:09:00,159
Courage is the true focus of our attention

177
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,840
Let's give a round of applause for this female warrior

178
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,960
Another young lady

179
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:12,159
Fam

180
00:09:12,159 --> 00:09:13,840
I give up. I'm too scared to jump

181
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:15,639
Too scared to jump, so I'll dance instead

182
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,600
Look, so many people are watching the DJ girl too

183
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,440
She's so confident

184
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:24,360
Confident people become the focus wherever they are

185
00:09:25,759 --> 00:09:27,559
They all seem to be shining

186
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,919
They're all so eye-catching

187
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:32,960
In comparison

188
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,360
I always thought

189
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,039
dressing beautifully would win attention

190
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,519
What a shallow thought

191
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,960
I really feel ashamed

192
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,399
Why isn't Gui Fang here yet?

193
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,799
Yeah, where is Gui Fang?

194
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:46,519
Exactly

195
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:47,200
Where is she?

196
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:48,639
Should I give her a call to check?

197
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:49,559
Sure, give her a call

198
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:50,440
Haven't seen her in a while

199
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,759
So cute

200
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:55,320
Gangzi

201
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,480
Is that you, Gangzi?

202
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,440
Who do you think it is?

203
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:00,720
Fang'er

204
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,039
Why is it you?

205
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:02,919
Oh my god

206
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,000
You're gonna get heatstroke in this

207
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,000
It's fine, it's fine

208
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,080
Why is it so thick?

209
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,080
It's just a little hardship

210
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,720
What hardship? Why suffer?

211
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:13,360
Hardship is meant for those who can take it

212
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:14,279
You say it's nothing

213
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,240
but why put ourselves through that?

214
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,519
Last time. It's the last time

215
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:20,600
Tell that Student Council senior to have a heart

216
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,159
You must be burning up, Fang'er

217
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:24,919
I'm fine

218
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:25,799
It's okay, it's okay, Fang Fang

219
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:27,240
You didn't see them do the East Lake Jump, did you?

220
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:27,960
No

221
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,799
It was really fun

222
00:10:28,799 --> 00:10:29,679
I recorded it all. Look

223
00:10:29,759 --> 00:10:32,279
Even the schedule for this event was made by you

224
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,639
Doesn't that mean you're the only one working?

225
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,000
Those who can, do more

226
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:39,600
It's also a validation of my abilities

227
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:40,679
No, if you ask me

228
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,399
menial tasks like running errands

229
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:44,480
you should just let the freshmen do it

230
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:47,799
Unlike your school, which has so much talent

231
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:49,639
The new people at our school

232
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,799
aren't much use yet

233
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,840
These kids nowadays

234
00:10:59,080 --> 00:10:59,960
lack initiative

235
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:02,759
Damn Gangzi

236
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,399
If I see you bullying Gui Fang again

237
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,799
watch out or I'll kick you to the moon

238
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:06,399
Wear it yourself

239
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:08,879
Hurry up

240
00:11:15,399 --> 00:11:15,919
Look

241
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,480
They jumped pretty far

242
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:17,960
Yeah

243
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,399
The entry was super clean

244
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:22,720
So brave

245
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:27,480
This girl's form is perfect

246
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,320
Yeah, this girl

247
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,279
was especially elegant when hitting the water

248
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:30,039
You guys wait for me a moment

249
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:30,919
I'll be right back

250
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:31,759
Okay

251
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:39,240
Xiaorui

252
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,919
Xiaorui is ignoring me too

253
00:11:55,039 --> 00:11:56,279
Welcome back to

254
00:11:56,639 --> 00:11:59,200
the East Lake Jump event site

255
00:11:59,519 --> 00:12:01,720
Look, it's our goddess senior,

256
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,799
Sister Xurui

257
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,000
She's so classy

258
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,919
She's just wearing a simple shirt,

259
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:08,320
yet she stands out so much in the crowd

260
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,919
She is really beautiful

261
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:11,960
That's her for you

262
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:14,120
This is what a goddess should look like

263
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,519
Don't be timid! Don't back down!

264
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:19,039
Show us your confidence and courage!

265
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:22,679
The second half will be even more exciting and spectacular!

266
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:27,759
Where is Xiao Yin?

267
00:12:27,759 --> 00:12:28,480
Come on!

268
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:29,519
Where is Xiao Yin?

269
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:30,080
Xiao Yin!

270
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,840
Wasn't Xiao Yin just here?

271
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:32,919
Didn't she go look for you?

272
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:34,440
Look, guys!

273
00:12:34,759 --> 00:12:35,600
Someone's about to pull a stunt!

274
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,440
Is the track ready?

275
00:12:37,679 --> 00:12:38,879
But before that, I want to see

276
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:40,399
if you guys are ready!

277
00:12:40,399 --> 00:12:41,240
Who is this?

278
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,360
Xiaocan

279
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:43,600
Xiaocan

280
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,440
Who is Xiaocan?

281
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,360
He's my cousin

282
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:52,080
Cousin! Cousin! Cousin!

283
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:58,840
Cousin! Cousin! Cousin!

284
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,879
Go!

285
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,679
Get ready!

286
00:13:05,399 --> 00:13:06,000
Here it comes!

287
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:07,879
Here goes nothing

288
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:08,600
Let's do this!

289
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,919
I am Kong Xiaocan!

290
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:14,080
