578
00:27:19,839 --> 00:27:20,359
We're even.

579
00:27:20,759 --> 00:27:21,160
Let's turn the page.

580
00:27:52,039 --> 00:27:52,720
Xiao Yin.

581
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:55,559
Xiao Yin, wake up.

582
00:28:05,359 --> 00:28:05,920
Wake up.

583
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:09,240
How did we get back yesterday?

584
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:10,920
I don't know.

585
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:15,839
Where is this?

586
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,079
This is my house.

587
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:27,680
I think I dreamed about Kong Xiaocan yesterday.

588
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:46,559
Don't we have Tri-Field Class today?

589
00:28:49,799 --> 00:28:50,359
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

590
00:28:50,839 --> 00:28:52,200
Don't... don't sleep. We're late.

591
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:53,640
Hurry, hurry, hurry. Get... get up.

592
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:54,640
What is it?

593
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,880
Change clothes. Tri-Field Class.

594
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:56,599
We're late.

595
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,000
My head is spinning.

596
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:00,559
What class?

597
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:01,720
Tri-Field Class.

598
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:03,200
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

599
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:05,000
Xiao Yin, hurry up.

600
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:05,720
Wait, something's wrong.

601
00:29:05,720 --> 00:29:06,240
We're late!

602
00:29:06,240 --> 00:29:07,160
I wasn't dreaming.

603
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:08,799
I think I really saw Kong Xiaocan.

604
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,000
Why was he at your house?

605
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,400
He's my cousin.

606
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:17,880
Why didn't you say so earlier?

607
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:19,519
You never asked me.

608
00:29:20,319 --> 00:29:21,079
Xiao Yin, hurry up.

609
00:29:22,559 --> 00:29:24,119
Great, the teacher isn't here yet. We're not late.

610
00:29:24,119 --> 00:29:24,720
Gui Fang is here.

611
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:26,319
She made the front page of the school forum yesterday.

612
00:29:26,319 --> 00:29:26,920
Did you guys know?

613
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:29,240
Saw it. Joke of the year.

614
00:29:29,279 --> 00:29:29,599
Fang'er.

615
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:30,680
That video was hilarious.

616
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:31,480
What took you so long?

617
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:34,119
Did you sleep until now, Xiao Yin?

618
00:29:34,359 --> 00:29:35,039
Look, quick.

619
00:29:35,799 --> 00:29:36,599
It sprouted! It sprouted!

620
00:29:36,599 --> 00:29:37,240
Stop filming.

621
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:39,000
I'm about to puke bean sprouts too.

622
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:41,839
Take it easy.

623
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:44,400
How much did you drink?

624
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:45,160
Quick, look.

625
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:46,759
It really sprouted.

626
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:49,119
Yeah, why have all of yours sprouted?

627
00:29:49,119 --> 00:29:50,440
Mine haven't done a thing.

628
00:29:50,440 --> 00:29:51,240
None of yours have?

629
00:29:51,319 --> 00:29:52,079
No.

630
00:29:52,759 --> 00:29:53,720
Can I dig one up?

631
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,160
Junior

632
00:30:18,519 --> 00:30:19,000
I'm busy

633
00:30:21,759 --> 00:30:22,920
I was just saying hi

634
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,480
Classmate, could you...

635
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:25,880
No

636
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:29,920
Xiao Cao

637
00:30:30,759 --> 00:30:33,160
Please do your own work from now on

638
00:30:33,160 --> 00:30:33,960
Okay?

639
00:30:34,079 --> 00:30:34,559
Xiao... Xiao...

640
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:35,839
Xiao Cao?

641
00:30:37,079 --> 00:30:38,480
You don't call me Senior anymore?

642
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,200
I'm not slacking off

643
00:30:41,559 --> 00:30:43,200
I'm giving the rookies a chance to practice

644
00:30:43,519 --> 00:30:44,839
I'm just distributing the work

645
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:46,799
Stop making empty promises

646
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:48,680
You're a perfectly good college student

647
00:30:48,839 --> 00:30:50,240
Can't you do something proper?

648
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:53,920
I don't know where you learned these bad habits

649
00:30:54,519 --> 00:30:55,200
Let me tell you

650
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:57,200
I'm the only one who'd tell you this now

651
00:30:57,359 --> 00:30:58,319
Once you enter the real world

652
00:30:58,480 --> 00:30:59,720
You'll suffer if you act like this

653
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:00,279
You know?

654
00:31:02,759 --> 00:31:03,720
Did you hear me?

655
00:31:05,359 --> 00:31:06,240
I really heard you

656
00:31:06,799 --> 00:31:07,160
Really

657
00:31:10,119 --> 00:31:10,480
Fine

658
00:31:11,079 --> 00:31:11,400
Go on

659
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:16,279
Why do I want to call her Mom?

660
00:31:24,079 --> 00:31:24,440
Gui Fang

661
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:25,559
Gui Fang

662
00:31:27,079 --> 00:31:27,839
You've gone viral

663
00:31:36,799 --> 00:31:37,200
Xiao Yin

664
00:31:38,119 --> 00:31:38,960
Xiao Yin, look

665
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,359
No

666
00:31:42,799 --> 00:31:45,160
It's a lifetime of dark history

667
00:31:45,359 --> 00:31:45,720
Look

668
00:31:46,279 --> 00:31:47,559
It's only been up for an hour

669
00:31:47,799 --> 00:31:49,240
Shares and likes are already over a thousand

670
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,799
That's really great

671
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:15,799
Mom is just like you now

672
00:32:32,359 --> 00:32:32,759
Mom

673
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:34,799
I'm proud of you too

674
00:32:39,039 --> 00:32:40,119
But letting loose for once

675
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,279
Feels pretty good

676
00:34:11,599 --> 00:34:12,800
Jumping when you can't swim

677
00:34:14,119 --> 00:34:14,840
Dummy
